<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Welcome to the CTM Demo</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        background-color: #f0f2f5;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .container {
        background: white;
        padding: 40px 60px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 90%;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #2c3e50;
        font-size: 2.5em;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.1em;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      li a {
        display: block;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        padding: 15px 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      }
      li a:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      .note {
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #7f8c8d;
      }
      .note a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .note a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to the CTM Demo</h1>
      <p>This application demonstrates various ways to integrate CallTrackingMetrics phone functionality into your web application.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/phone">Embedded Phone in CRM Demo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/agent-status">Agent Status</a></li>
        <li><a href="/dialer-only">Outbound Dialer Only (Custom UI Example)</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="note">Please <a href="/login">log in</a> to access pages that require authentication, such as the CRM demo.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>